   <body>
      <p>After you logged in, you are navigated to the Home page. Home page displays program details for all the created programs, as shown in the below image.</p>
      <p>
         <fig>
            <image placement="break"
                   width="700"
                   href="../attachments/102432688/102432737.jpg"/>
         </fig>
      </p>
      <p>You can perform following actions on the Home page:</p>
      <p>
         <table>
            <tgroup cols="2">
               <colspec colname="col1"/>
               <colspec colname="col2"/>
               <thead>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Field</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>User Action</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </thead>
               <tbody>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>New Program</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Click New Program button to create a new program.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Select View</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Select the required option from the Select View drop-down list to set your desired view of the page.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Search Filter</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Select Search Filters to specify filter criteria and fields to display.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
                  <row>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Display</p>
                     </entry>
                     <entry>
                        <p>Select Display option to set the number of the programs to be displayed on the home page.</p>
                     </entry>
                  </row>
               </tbody>
            </tgroup>
         </table>
      </p>
